remarks: Lemma for ~ nodense .  If one surreal is older than another, then there is an ordinal at which they are not equal.  (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 16-Jun-2011.)
statement:
nodenselem3 $p |- ( ( A e. No /\ B e. No ) -> ( ( bday ` A ) e. ( bday ` B ) -> E. a e. On ( A ` a ) =/= ( B ` a ) ) ) $.
$d A a $.
$d B a $.
